Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.39,0:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.47,0:00:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「1889年娜蒂亞的世界之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好！我是強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是娜蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.45,0:01:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次是介紹我們所處的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.59,0:01:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾菲爾鐵塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.36,0:01:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們認識的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座塔是為了1889年舉行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.14,0:01:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎萬國博覽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.24,0:01:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由亞歷山大．吉斯達．艾菲爾先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所設計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.50,0:01:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花費了17個月才建造起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高度…居然有312公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.34,0:01:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看吧！這種氣派…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…被"紅色諾亞"…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連同巴黎街市一起破壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.38,0:01:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…在我不知道的期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生過這種事啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.36,0:01:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.02,0:01:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後，西元1895年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又再度重建了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也還是命名為大艾菲爾鐵塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！不是完全一樣嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是把一樣的東西修好而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.30,0:01:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太平常了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也別這麼說嘛！來！接下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊！這些…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我和叔叔製造的飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華．多．拉謝努系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！這些…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都失敗了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…請不用擔心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是世界第一架飛上天空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝載動力裝置的飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華．多．拉謝努八世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水平尾翼和後掠翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活塞式雙汽缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭載有回轉式引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像翅膀的構造…怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常了不起的構造啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！就沒有別的話好說了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，介紹下一個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不認識嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是儒勒．凡爾納先生啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金克魯被擄？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是儒勒．凡爾納！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在西元1872年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發表「海底兩萬里」的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有「神秘島」…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「環遊世界八十天」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「地底旅行」「月球旅行」等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,許多空想科幻小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起的人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我們處在的1889年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還早好幾年，就寫了關於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鸚鵡螺號"的潛艇小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定，尼莫船長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是看了這本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才決定自己的化名和船的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.22,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.49,0:03:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.13,0:03:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.13,0:03:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「這就是新亞特蘭蒂斯！之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.61,0:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(雷聲，響徹於永遠的大地…)\N(新亞特蘭蒂斯)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.24,0:04:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(卡格依總統)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離現在大約1萬2千年前\N(卡格依總統)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界在眾神之國的支配下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,享受著和平\N(這個影像是有關於新亞特蘭蒂斯的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.48,0:04:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(這個影像是有關於新亞特蘭蒂斯的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個眾神之國\N(這個影像是有關於新亞特蘭蒂斯的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.45,0:04:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(這個影像是有關於新亞特蘭蒂斯的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是舊亞特蘭蒂斯帝國\N(極為少數的資料其中之一)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(極為少數的資料其中之一)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不幸的…這個國度…\N(並且，關於本片的提供者)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(並且，關於本片的提供者)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一晝夜間就被毀滅了…\N(並且，關於本片的提供者)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(由於許多的因素而無法公開)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.49,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…愚蠢的奴僕，人類們…\N(由於許多的因素而無法公開)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有了世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.96,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧！這種渾沌的世界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奴僕們…在這1萬2千年之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷重複愚蠢的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直可說只達到「不可能」而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此繼續放任下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球會整個毀滅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…這就要結束了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我們所支配的眾神之國…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將以新亞特蘭蒂斯之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.03,0:05:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奴僕們的面前再度復活！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N("神之魚"艦隊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們目前…\N(戰鬥人型坦克)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(戰鬥人型坦克)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於繼承舊亞特蘭蒂斯之超武器\N(戰鬥人型坦克)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於繼承舊亞特蘭蒂斯之超武器\N(空中艦隊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而集結成…\N(空中艦隊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大軍事組織\N(閱兵典禮)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.51,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成果將再度呈現於尼歐皇帝面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻擾這條路之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將由復活的巴比倫塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處以天罰之光！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是受選之民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.16,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸位！世界的黎明不遠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影片就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新亞特蘭蒂斯的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自1890年以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也未曾在歷史舞台上出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這意味著組織的解體嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是潛伏於地下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將再度向我們挑戰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使經過了一個多世紀的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然無法真相大白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NHK特集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的惡夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三夜  「巴黎飛碟事件」  終
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.26,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「萬能潛艇"鸚鵡螺號"的26個秘密！之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,１. 大小！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鸚鵡螺號"全長150公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.38,0:07:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水中排水量12000噸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯角式潛艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相當於戰艦的船能夠潛進海裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起的科學技術！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,２. 動力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鸚鵡螺號"裝置的機型是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾斯提克式常溫對消滅引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將海中的氫分離出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這時候產生的反應粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在中心相撞擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成對的消滅掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.12,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上能量交流接收器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將對消滅能源直接轉變成電力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或運動能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一點也不會浪費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.07,0:08:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…科學的勝利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,３. 攻擊武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對潛誘導彈以及飛行爆雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.33,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是"鸚鵡螺號"的主要武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射管總共有40具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起！只要有了這些…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"神之魚"也只能…束手待斃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.90,0:08:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,４. 防禦武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.22,0:08:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對雷擊防禦系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈防禦彈全部共有10萬個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是怎樣的魚雷都打不中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,５. 船體構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鸚鵡螺號"的船殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.33,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙金屬，太空鈦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透明部分是結晶構造體的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「硬化水晶」(結晶體)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關部是用最堅固的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超硬鑽石纖維(多重層式)做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…像宇宙金屬這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球上是無法做出來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼弄到手的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘…密…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.63,0:09:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,６、７、８、９、１０…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？伊萊克特小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的秘密呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘…密…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強，什麼事都要別人來告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不行的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了！尼莫船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就下次再見了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.86,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「BLUE WATER的大秘密！之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.95,0:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟…究竟…究竟是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(BLUE WATER的秘密)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這BLUE WATER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是不會發光呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼敲它、燒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒一點反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是娜蒂亞不在旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它就不會發光也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了！注意到重要的地方了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不是阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是姊姊才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過了二十歲的人都是阿姨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太囂張了…最近的小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了…原諒小孩子的天真無邪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是大人的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜、冷靜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨， 快點來說明原因嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就正如剛才瑪麗所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE WATER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是繼承舊亞特蘭蒂斯王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血統的人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會發揮它的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.27,0:11:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(BLUE WATER)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…\N(BLUE WATER)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.37,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞就是亞特蘭蒂斯的公主囉\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞就是亞特蘭蒂斯的公主囉\N(舊亞特蘭蒂斯王國)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.61,0:12:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(舊亞特蘭蒂斯王國)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.81,0:12:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事\N(舊亞特蘭蒂斯王國)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(舊亞特蘭蒂斯王國)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.11,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…那種任性女孩會是公主\N(舊亞特蘭蒂斯王國)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…那種任性女孩會是公主\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界也真是沒救了\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界也真是沒救了\N(公主?娜蒂亞)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.32,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(公主?娜蒂亞)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE WATER也希望\N(公主?娜蒂亞)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.69,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有選擇主人的權利呢\N(公主?娜蒂亞)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有選擇主人的權利呢\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過話又說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE WATER到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…首先先看看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼紋路在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…注意到重要的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為BLUE WATER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嵌有光電腦的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,構成基盤的部份用肉眼看上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會像是三次元(立體)花紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…BLUE WATER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是用什麼做成的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.65,0:12:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是用叫綠晶體的金屬集合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面光能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以固體的形狀保存著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…不就是能源的硬塊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此，回答得非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且對亞特蘭蒂斯人來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死之後靈魂會回到BLUE WATER之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE WATER就好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬用刀具墳墓，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的比喻方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說，到底亞特蘭蒂斯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是地球外的文明種族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在想些什麼根本沒人能瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以娜蒂亞也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是所有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都像冰溶化了似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.47,0:13:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰溶化、冰溶化…這個樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就下次再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其五
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 在你眼中有許許多多的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比一切都更加燦爛耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.76,0:15:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議　海的娜蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.77,0:15:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭軟弱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要辜負了廣闊的青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.78,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在進入夢鄉前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望展翅飛翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.65,0:15:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開心裡的音樂盒　讓它響出旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.89,0:15:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點點地奏出了幸福與勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.53,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 在你眼中有許許多多的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.71,0:15:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,言語代表永遠的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.75,0:16:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了在心裡去嘗試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.55,0:16:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛比珠寶更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.72,0:16:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比一切都更加燦爛耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間正當西元1889年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞他們在偶然搭上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.46,0:16:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬能潛艇"鸚鵡螺號"上的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然繼續著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也仍然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤著新亞特蘭蒂斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鸚鵡螺號"的航海仍在繼續著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「娜蒂亞、參加選美大會之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是…第2名是依可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第3名是格蘭蒂斯吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊…我只是偷聽來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾可先生他們好像在策劃舉行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸚鵡螺號小姐的選美比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以了…事前預計…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有同好會的依可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像非常有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那第一名呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是…伊萊克特小姐呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不行！像那種年紀大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要像這種…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.48,0:17:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕…是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…是瑪麗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪…瑪…瑪麗…與其說是年輕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說是太年幼了吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…艾可先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會是那種人嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.84,0:17:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強會投我的票，對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會投我的票，對不對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這種事…是主觀的問題啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有強的一票，我就己經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一票是國王的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…我…我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…投…伊萊克特小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個真的也不是國王投的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…究竟會是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.48,0:19:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.84,0:19:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心底深處的焦躁  該如何是好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠的夢  就快要看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.75,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喃喃低語著仰望夜空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.92,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在流星的彼方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光芒耀眼的映著  與你的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.96,0:19:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRY  安慰的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.80,0:19:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是無法觸及心靈的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.87,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有懷抱著的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.81,0:19:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會越來越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因為是自己決定的的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.99,0:19:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算孤獨一個人  大概也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算走投無路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不知何去何從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.76,0:20:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也還會有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.76,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其六
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.66,0:20:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「歡迎來到新亞特蘭蒂斯之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.52,0:21:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎！來到新亞特蘭蒂斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為大家帶路的卡格依
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的特別來賓是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.86,0:21:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.26,0:21:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來還有國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了…也罷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的目的是對我們的工作態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有所瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.77,0:21:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以隨便問叔叔任何問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！大叔，那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.24,0:21:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔～這個問題問得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.38,0:21:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個正是由我們的科學設計的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬能土木機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不死軍隊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人型坦克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難看啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，那個呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.43,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們引以為傲的高速飛行船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.67,0:21:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"卡魯卡洛頓"啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家老太勞頓了！？(諧音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的說，卡魯卡洛頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拉丁語中是為被握住的形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說被"卡魯卡洛頓"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.68,0:22:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握住的人是為了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.65,0:22:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一大堆船！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.62,0:22:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是"神之魚號"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.15,0:22:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用了古代亞特蘭蒂斯的超科學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.72,0:22:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們所建造的潛艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.06,0:22:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用Ｌ引擎的水流噴射器來推進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.56,0:22:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全長１４８公尺的攻擊型潛艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他也還有Mark Ⅱ型的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.70,0:22:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔！海星飛過來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.54,0:22:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！這正是我們引以為傲的空中戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.74,0:22:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿載著從世界各地發掘出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古代的超級兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.45,0:22:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基部運用反重力系統在天空飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.38,0:22:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是無敵的空中移動要塞啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.65,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多人在工作啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.62,0:22:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，叔叔們是在尼歐皇帝之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了建設和平的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.53,0:22:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日夜不停的努力著啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.77,0:23:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常忙碌啊…讓你輕鬆點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.34,0:23:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看！那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終兵器…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.78,0:23:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫塔第２爐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！是啊！最初的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.62,0:23:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被"鸚鵡螺號"破壞了是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！不對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是技術上的問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.19,0:23:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是輸給尼莫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要等這個再度完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.44,0:23:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在天上的12個「下僕之星」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.71,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對全世界的任何地方進行攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.61,0:23:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將在軍事、經濟…各個方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.51,0:23:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配愚蠢的人類們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.71,0:23:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引導他們走上正確的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.65,0:23:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我們非去做不可的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為造物主的使命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？瑪麗君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.93,0:24:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！快昏倒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.61,0:24:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫塔的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.48,0:24:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自爆裝置…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.18,0:24:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.45,0:24:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.59,0:24:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨鐵匠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.49,0:24:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到山裡　就是火燒山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.66,0:24:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掃地出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.87,0:24:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.90,0:25:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.57,0:25:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.57,0:25:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「娜蒂亞超百科之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.54,0:25:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是娜蒂亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.51,0:25:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾所周知的娜蒂亞的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.64,0:25:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人在度過自己的人生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.58,0:25:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這一生之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.65,0:25:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟會認識多少女性呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.45,0:25:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個數目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.62,0:25:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會隨著個人的認同而有所差異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.72,0:25:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是像這樣的任性、固執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.76,0:25:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好惡極其極端的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.66,0:25:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是不會再有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.30,0:25:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.67,0:25:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們的女主角，娜蒂亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.57,0:25:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個娜蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.50,0:25:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼樣的女性呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.61,0:25:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先從她的基本資料來看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.64,0:26:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全名：娜蒂亞．拉．阿魯沃魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.65,0:26:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西元1875年5月31日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.32,0:26:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於現在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.59,0:26:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舊塔爾特蘇斯王國遺址誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.62,0:26:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙子座　A型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.32,0:26:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身高155公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.53,0:26:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體重43公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.60,0:26:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸圍79　腰圍58　臀圍83
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.83,0:26:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子的尺碼是22.5公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.84,0:26:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒指的尺寸是7號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.64,0:26:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅長踩大球、騎獨輪車、游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.71,0:26:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡吃的食物，例如雞蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.85,0:26:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是要全素的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.55,0:26:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐、素什錦之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.65,0:26:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西，例如肉、魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.66,0:26:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但照她自己的說法是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.59,0:26:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些不是食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.69,0:26:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能算是偏食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.63,0:26:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青椒、洋蔥、香菇才算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.73,0:26:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是這些也是夠任性的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.77,0:26:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就她的性格來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.54,0:26:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.51,0:27:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的任性實在是大災難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.11,0:27:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在過去像這樣任性的女主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.45,0:27:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是沒有的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.71,0:27:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倔強、還要加上頑固…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.68,0:27:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上還是人生觀悲觀的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.69,0:27:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是以什麼樣的想法活著的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.66,0:27:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們訪問了她的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.19,0:27:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年強．洛克．羅狄克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.40,0:27:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強．洛克．羅狄克君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.73,0:27:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在弄不懂啊…女孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.70,0:27:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概只有這樣的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.50,0:27:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能忍受娜蒂亞的折磨吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.61,0:27:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生出這樣帶給他人困擾的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.54,0:27:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟她的親屬是什麼樣的想法呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.65,0:27:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訪問她的親生父親的尼莫船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.59,0:27:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫（假名）船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.42,0:27:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.59,0:27:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的不負責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.59,0:27:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說「老鼠的孩子會打洞」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.56,0:27:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是指這種意思吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.50,0:27:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是娜蒂亞的繼母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.67,0:28:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是尼莫船長續絃的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.73,0:28:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自稱伊萊克特的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.87,0:28:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想進行採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.61,0:28:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是結果非常遺憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.91,0:28:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊萊克特（假名）副船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.51,0:28:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可奉告！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.78,0:28:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.65,0:28:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣薄情的環境中長大的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.65,0:28:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能不能成長為大人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.49,0:28:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.72,0:28:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是指能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.56,0:28:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不被感情所控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.73,0:28:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能尊重自己以外他人的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.73,0:28:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.73,0:28:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和別人一起活下去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.73,0:28:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞能成為像這樣的人的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.37,0:28:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的會來到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.11,0:28:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種可能性還是有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.57,0:28:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某監督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.71,0:28:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某位動畫監督是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.68,0:28:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這一天就算真的會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.78,0:28:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到底要等到什麼時候呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.08,0:29:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞超百科　終
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.42,0:29:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:56.32,0:29:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.49,0:30:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「夕陽鏘鏘(第52回) 之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.24,0:30:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.44,0:30:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是會員號碼4號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.61,0:30:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強.洛克.羅狄克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.37,0:30:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是會員號碼16號的娜蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.84,0:30:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次要為各位介紹令人懷念的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.61,0:30:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,許多生活照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.95,0:30:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是…這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.92,0:30:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.49,0:30:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是馬戲團時代的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.92,0:30:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣…真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.66,0:30:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好陰沉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.80,0:30:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人總是會遇到很多事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.83,0:30:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也總會有…情緒低落的時候啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.24,0:30:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再接下去看吧！接下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.31,0:30:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是國王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.74,0:30:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候看起來還像動物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.54,0:30:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了南國之島之後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.48,0:30:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.28,0:30:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.82,0:30:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我的眼光…有什麼要批評的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.22,0:31:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.85,0:31:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，再下來是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.62,0:31:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是娜蒂亞的早餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.66,0:31:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是午餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.06,0:31:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.63,0:31:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，就這樣每天重複啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.43,0:31:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃不厭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.47,0:31:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃不厭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:17.84,0:31:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有其它的食物了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.71,0:31:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.21,0:31:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是"鸚鵡螺號"啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.31,0:31:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是還存在的時候的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.68,0:31:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是秘密的船…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:28.58,0:31:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還真是留了不少的照片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.72,0:31:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.79,0:31:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等了好久啊！伊萊克特小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.19,0:31:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:38.59,0:31:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.69,0:31:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…真好啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.26,0:31:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然成年人的魅力是不一樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.13,0:31:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.93,0:31:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我在這之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.34,0:31:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈馬哈馬被我的魅力害得好苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.14,0:31:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一…定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.77,0:31:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我覺得是倒過來才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.01,0:32:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.61,0:32:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗和3人組呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.48,0:32:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.62,0:32:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種團體生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.22,0:32:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的「青春」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.36,0:32:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.59,0:32:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連這種的都有？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.70,0:32:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.90,0:32:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種照片是什麼時候照的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.43,0:32:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…這些…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大打擊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.44,0:32:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁心…骯髒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.41,0:32:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦！這些是…山姆拍的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.01,0:32:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就專挑這種地方等這種機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.38,0:32:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍這種照片看是不是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.52,0:32:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是男孩子，沒辦法啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.59,0:32:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開放的女人是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:42.19,0:32:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開放的男人就能看嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.72,0:32:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…女人的話就沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.86,0:32:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，因為是我才會這麼好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.06,0:32:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.23,0:32:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.36,0:32:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！這麼不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.63,0:32:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.87,0:32:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，這個是我睡著的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.00,0:32:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆偷偷拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.41,0:33:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不會少掉什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.84,0:33:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！說不行就不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.64,0:33:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！真不像男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.41,0:33:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿過來！快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.08,0:33:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(請稍後)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.38,0:33:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.85,0:33:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.88,0:33:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的小象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.45,0:33:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.36,0:33:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.66,0:33:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.63,0:33:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，告訴我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.76,0:33:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦！真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.16,0:33:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛！告訴我嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.50,0:33:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒關係！那麼就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.33,0:33:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.00,0:33:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.41,0:33:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！強這大笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:43.92,0:33:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…究竟是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.05,0:33:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還故作不知…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.12,0:33:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就裝作不知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.09,0:33:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.62,0:34:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.43,0:34:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:30.99,0:34:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「追尋失去的時光…之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.78,0:34:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊萊克特(假名)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.45,0:34:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鸚鵡螺號  副船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.18,0:34:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18歲(自稱)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.18,0:34:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾瑪迪克海戰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.45,0:34:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是行蹤不明的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.02,0:34:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.15,0:34:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候…被空中戰艦擊沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.86,0:35:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去浮力的主操縱區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.06,0:35:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深深沉入海溝的深處了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.03,0:35:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎對消滅引擎無法再啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:11.47,0:35:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的輔助電池也快用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:14.57,0:35:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上8千公尺的深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.84,0:35:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對遍體鱗傷的船體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.41,0:35:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫不容情施加壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.38,0:35:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都在漏水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.11,0:35:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連排水也不可能的狀態…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.05,0:35:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我們還剩下最後的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.39,0:35:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為很幸運的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.42,0:35:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇上深海洋流的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.56,0:35:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在洋流的源頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.76,0:35:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著古代亞特蘭蒂斯人建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.86,0:35:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海底隧道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.87,0:35:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能到那裡就有救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.90,0:35:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要進入海底隧道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.47,0:35:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須保存船的推進力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.61,0:35:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個只有保存所有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:53.18,0:35:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預備電源的電力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.48,0:35:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在很痛苦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.42,0:36:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有一點光的黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.65,0:36:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有像快被凍結住的寒冷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.42,0:36:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.26,0:36:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…也就是盡人事待天命了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.39,0:36:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:10.39,0:36:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以在精神的細絲就快斷的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.43,0:36:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到海底隧道的光亮時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.80,0:36:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.94,0:36:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能活著…原來是這樣的感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:23.54,0:36:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…真是太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.34,0:36:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.11,0:36:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了舊塔爾特蘇斯遺址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.25,0:36:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用"鸚鵡螺"的對消滅能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.22,0:36:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓發掘戰艦，艾克西利翁復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.09,0:36:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這個頭髮又是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.29,0:36:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，有些願望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.13,0:36:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.13,0:36:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後，對這種打扮還喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.13,0:36:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.33,0:36:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這是正式的宇宙裝束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.47,0:36:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…戴戒指了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.01,0:36:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.61,0:36:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:01.01,0:37:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.72,0:37:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東京都內  某日、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.52,0:37:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於池袋  嘈雜之酒屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.23,0:37:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「追尋失去的時光…之卷」終
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.46,0:37:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:55.23,0:37:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.50,0:38:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「比較誰強！！\N"新鸚鵡螺"對"紅色諾亞"之卷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.47,0:38:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,１.  大小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.18,0:38:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.91,0:38:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是萬能戰艦"新鸚鵡螺號"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.95,0:38:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全長333.33公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.69,0:38:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本重量3萬8千噸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.16,0:38:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超特級太空戰艦啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.63,0:38:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.50,0:38:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有舊"鸚鵡螺號"的2倍以上啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.97,0:38:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不過"紅色諾亞"是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.83,0:38:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直徑10公里20公尺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.07,0:38:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當斯基型飛碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.24,0:38:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小上輸了很多呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.71,0:38:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是愛好和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.04,0:38:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會勝利的，對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.91,0:38:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.92,0:38:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,２.  動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.38,0:38:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！這就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.69,0:38:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"新鸚鵡螺號"的主引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.29,0:38:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾菲斯型大型縮退爐嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.22,0:39:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！利用共有重力半徑回轉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.33,0:39:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個的小型黑洞以常溫凍結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.97,0:39:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將產生出來的奇點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.27,0:39:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把彼此之間半徑的誤差消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.07,0:39:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這時候發生的能源取出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.87,0:39:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高性能引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.81,0:39:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.34,0:39:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全不懂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.31,0:39:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能容忍愚蠢的人！傻瓜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.85,0:39:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…伊萊克特小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.05,0:39:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.15,0:39:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:28.19,0:39:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"紅色諾亞"也裝載了縮退爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:31.69,0:39:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以性能上是平分秋色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.96,0:39:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是正義的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.33,0:39:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不會輸的，對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.13,0:39:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.10,0:39:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,３.  攻擊武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.67,0:39:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好神氣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.30,0:39:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是武器圖是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.04,0:39:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！現在的"新鸚鵡螺號"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.11,0:39:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠使用這些武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.78,0:39:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…"紅色諾亞"…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.58,0:39:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有大約50倍於此的火力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.82,0:39:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.62,0:39:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好誇張…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:00.25,0:40:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器比例居然是50比1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.36,0:40:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果你相信自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.32,0:40:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會輸的,是麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.89,0:40:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.86,0:40:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,４.  防禦武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:12.20,0:40:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.63,0:40:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於我們也有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.80,0:40:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盼望已久的超電磁護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.77,0:40:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…不過很遺憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.11,0:40:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有完全修復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.04,0:40:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能維持1分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.04,0:40:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們會勇敢的面對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.51,0:40:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒問題的對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.08,0:40:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.12,0:40:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,５.  其它的武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.65,0:40:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！還有這麼多其他的武器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.16,0:40:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都用黑色遮掉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.83,0:40:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，兩方的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.46,0:40:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都屬於攻擊型母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:44.96,0:40:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是彼此都沒有剩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.93,0:40:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能修復的攻擊機或轟炸機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.14,0:40:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他還剩下這些東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.51,0:40:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，有啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.08,0:40:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？怎樣的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:58.01,0:40:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:59.45,0:40:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.88,0:41:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再慢慢的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:02.55,0:41:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告…訴…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.13,0:41:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.23,0:41:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附錄劇場就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.50,0:41:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位，要多保重啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.56,0:41:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見…見…見…見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:23.27,0:41:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞附錄劇場　終
